Resolution Insurance has unveiled a transit cover for marine cargo. The product &ndash; Resolution Marine Cargo &ndash; provides tailor-made solutions to meet marine cargo insurance needs for freight, logistics and shipping, clearing and forwarding companies. The services are also available for agencies directly importing and exporting goods.The insurance policy covers accidental loss or damage to goods in transit by sea, air and land, and can be bought through an online portal. &ldquo;With the growing popularity and convenience of online commerce, customers can buy Resolution Marine Cargo when importing merchandise anywhere around the world,&rdquo; managing director Alice Mwai said.She said the decision to launch the cover is in line with the insurer&rsquo;s business strategy on product diversification and increasing insurance penetration.